    [caption id="attachment_2377" align="alignnone" width="300"]<a href="http://martinusadyh.web.id/gallery/?album=9&amp;gallery=7&amp;pid=378"><img src="http://martinusadyh.web.id/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Lokasi-Kita-Mengambil-Photo-300x225.jpg" alt="Lokasi Kita Mengambil Photo" width="300" height="225" class="size-medium wp-image-2377" /></a> Lokasi Kita Mengambil Photo[/caption]
    </td>
